  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6422890">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6422890/" class="title-link">百年海军</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6422890"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/79171607/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u79171607-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/79171607/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">雪枫竹</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-11-20"
      class="main-meta">2013-11-20 23:39:00</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6422890_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  都说一年陆军十年空军百年海军， 百年，更需要人的积淀。人才是战争和军队的根本。 从甲午至抗日，中国海军经历了一个从物质上由盛转衰，但从战斗精神上由衰转胜的洗礼。 这才铸就了海军的灵魂。 幸好新旧交替，海军并未断代，哪怕物质上是从土坑里头白手起家，但是精神上的延...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6422890_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6422890_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










